    "title": "From days to minutes: Making population estimates faster and smarter",
    "excerpt": "<p>The Office of Data and Innovation (ODI) helped improve how the Department of Finance (Finance) makes small-area population estimates, supporting statewide resource planning. Project scope Partner Methods The opportunity Finance makes small-area population estimates. The state uses them to distribute funds and plan infrastructure and services. A key dataset used for this is building footprints, &#8230; <a title=\"From days to minutes: Making population estimates faster and smarter\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://live-digital-ca-gov.pantheonsite.io/our-work/projects/from-days-minutes-making-population-estimates-faster-smarter/\" aria-label=\"More on From days to minutes: Making population estimates faster and smarter\">Read more</a></p>\n",
